  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save Ukraine from the hordes of swamp savages in this action-adventure game with physics-based combat and lowbrow dark comedy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics-based combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of interactable objects that you can use as a weapon.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detailed dismemberment and satisfying physics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Funny story with lowbrow dark comedy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjustable difficulty, change enemies amount/speed/health as you wish.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game made by one person - may contain bugs and other issues.</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save Ukraine from the hordes of swamp savages in this action-adventure game with physics-based combat and lowbrow dark comedy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics-based combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of interactable objects that you can use as a weapon.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detailed dismemberment and satisfying physics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Funny story with lowbrow dark comedy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjustable difficulty, change enemies amount/speed/health as you wish.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game made by one person - may contain bugs and other issues.</h2>",
